en_189773_0	The mortal remains of a veteran filmmaker, Dr. Lester James Peiris is currently lying at the Independence Square until 3 pm.
en_189773_1	The state funeral will begin at 4 pm.
en_189773_2	The government has declared today as a national day of mourning in respect of the veteran film-maker.
en_189773_3	Having performed religious rites at his home on Lester James Peiris Mawatha, Colombo 5, the cortege left the residence at 10.45 this morning.
en_189773_4	Artistes received the coffin when the cortege arrived at the National Film Corporation on Bauddhaloka Mawatha.
